Prince '''Alexei Grigorievich Scherbatov''' ({{lang-ru|Алексей Григорьевич Щербатов}}; 1776-1848) was a Russian imperial general during the [[Napoleonic Wars]] and [[November Uprising]]. Born into a noble family, he served as [[Mayor of Moscow]] for the final five years of his life.
